**Problem 9 - Celsius to Fahrenheit Temperature Converter**\
Design a program that converts Celsius temperatures to Fahrenheit temperatures. The formula is as follows: F = 9/5C + 32. The program should ask the user to enter a temperature in Celsius, and then display the temperature converted to Fahrenheit.\
